## Questions to Ask Before Building Features
1. Does this help users filter by objective specs?
2. Can this be done client-side without a backend?
3. Will this still work in 5 years without maintenance?
4. Does this add value or just complexity?
5. Would I use this feature myself?

If you answer "no" to any of these, reconsider the feature.
